Class Admin

Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<Intranet.User>
public class Admin extends Intranet.Employee implements Serializable, Comparable<Intranet.User>
The Admin class represents admins' account in intranet system. This class used for managing users - add/remove/update operations. Can view users log files.
